---
title: Creamy Green Pesto & Bacon Fusilli with Leek, Baby Broccoli & Plant-Based Parmesan
description: You can add just about anything to a pasta, an entire veggie garden can be chopped up and tossed through a rich sauce.Sometimes, simple really is best though. Leek, baby broccoli and a little spinach in a cream, bacon and pesto sauce is all this dish needs to leave you feeling full and oh-so happy.
